WEBVTT

1
00:00:08.655 --> 00:00:12.550
DORM
I still remember the first time I left home.

2
00:00:17.455 --> 00:00:20.522
It was a Sunday afternoon...

3
00:00:20.592 --> 00:00:22.380
that felt both hectic and lonely.

4
00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:27.687
It was the last day...

5
00:00:28.560 --> 00:00:32.619
of the mid-term break for me
and my seventh grade friends.

6
00:00:35.535 --> 00:00:37.543
It felt like the last day of freedom...

7
00:00:38.288 --> 00:00:41.484
A freedom we'd come to enjoy during our vacation.

8
00:00:42.352 --> 00:00:43.148
Stop crying!

9
00:00:43.504 --> 00:00:45.154
You didn't get any work done over vacation.

10
00:00:49.872 --> 00:00:51.082
One thing I felt that...

11
00:00:52.080 --> 00:00:55.974
I'd never come to terms with is...

12
00:00:56.432 --> 00:00:58.197
- How do you want it cut. handsome?
- Crew cut.

13
00:00:59.280 --> 00:01:00.622
The last day of vacation...

14
00:01:07.119 --> 00:01:07.751
Even so...

15
00:01:08.208 --> 00:01:10.696
some of us can't wait for school to re-open...

16
00:01:12.848 --> 00:01:14.790
because it means being
reunited with our friends.

17
00:01:21.423 --> 00:01:22.154
Except for me.

18
00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:30.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

19
00:01:32.816 --> 00:01:34.125
Hey! Stop pressing the buttons!

20
00:01:57.936 --> 00:02:00.173
Jaew! Pen! Take good care of the house!

21
00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:01.454
Yes. ma'am.

22
00:02:09.615 --> 00:02:11.694
You know. we could've waited for Ton...

23
00:02:11.695 --> 00:02:14.035
to finish 7th grade before
transferring him to another school.

24
00:02:15.279 --> 00:02:18.254
The sudden move is a shock for me as well.

25
00:02:18.255 --> 00:02:20.459
Listen. this isn't open for discussion. understand?

26
00:02:21.776 --> 00:02:23.631
Ton's new school is up-country right. Dad?

27
00:02:23.919 --> 00:02:24.967
Yes. it's in Chonburi. son.

28
00:02:25.839 --> 00:02:27.563
Where will he sleep?

29
00:02:27.855 --> 00:02:28.902
In the school dormitory.

30
00:02:29.744 --> 00:02:30.780
They have everything there.

31
00:02:31.376 --> 00:02:33.929
Remember. son. a man
must be able to live anywhere.

32
00:02:38.415 --> 00:02:39.757
Are we almost there?

33
00:02:40.495 --> 00:02:42.337
No. we have to cross the Bangpakong River first.

34
00:02:43.536 --> 00:02:44.910
Hurry up and make a wish. Toh!

35
00:02:44.976 --> 00:02:46.470
If you hold your breath as we cross the bridge...

36
00:02:46.736 --> 00:02:50.255
whatever you wish for will come true.

37
00:02:50.255 --> 00:02:50.888
Really. Mom?

38
00:02:51.215 --> 00:02:53.932
But don't cheat and sneak a breath first.

39
00:02:54.031 --> 00:02:55.029
Ton. hold your breath too.

40
00:03:19.055 --> 00:03:20.038
What did you wish for?

41
00:03:23.695 --> 00:03:26.216
For Dad to send me to boarding school with Ton.

42
00:03:28.976 --> 00:03:30.383
How about you. Ton?

43
00:03:36.112 --> 00:03:39.211
Saichon Witaya School

44
00:03:59.215 --> 00:04:00.644
Toh. play around here. okay?

45
00:04:27.344 --> 00:04:29.678
Student Dormitory

46
00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:37.161
Good afternoon. Teacher.

47
00:04:38.096 --> 00:04:39.241
I'm Miss Pranee...

48
00:04:40.016 --> 00:04:41.925
the dorm master for junior high boys.

49
00:04:43.215 --> 00:04:44.109
This must be Chatree.

50
00:04:45.008 --> 00:04:45.804
Yes. ma'am.

51
00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:48.294
Parents. please wait here.

52
00:04:49.168 --> 00:04:51.175
Chatree. follow me. please.

53
00:04:56.719 --> 00:04:57.668
Don't dilly dally now.

54
00:05:08.079 --> 00:05:09.159
Hey. it's a new kid.

55
00:05:10.896 --> 00:05:12.041
Where's he from?

56
00:05:14.255 --> 00:05:15.564
He seems like a troublemaker.

57
00:05:29.136 --> 00:05:30.380
This is your bed.

58
00:05:30.896 --> 00:05:32.456
Go collect your blanket.

59
00:05:33.776 --> 00:05:37.453
Make sure to make your bed every morning.

60
00:05:38.415 --> 00:05:40.139
Every boy must take care of himself here.

61
00:05:40.656 --> 00:05:43.972
No one will serve you or
pamper you like you were at home.

62
00:05:56.112 --> 00:05:57.737
Dad has written your name on everything.

63
00:06:00.975 --> 00:06:01.804
Study hard. son.

64
00:06:02.576 --> 00:06:03.983
Don't get into trouble. okay?

65
00:06:08.336 --> 00:06:09.333
Please keep an eye on him.

66
00:06:10.575 --> 00:06:11.174
I will.

67
00:07:29.488 --> 00:07:30.284
Don't be so noisy.

68
00:07:55.631 --> 00:07:57.573
Chatree. follow me.

69
00:08:05.872 --> 00:08:07.727
Dinner is served at 6 PM.

70
00:08:08.623 --> 00:08:09.998
Everyone must eat on time.

71
00:08:12.303 --> 00:08:14.474
This is your seat. Sit down.

72
00:08:35.919 --> 00:08:37.861
Next term. I'm sending Ton to boarding school.

73
00:08:41.583 --> 00:08:43.656
Why the sudden decision to send him away?

74
00:08:44.880 --> 00:08:45.578
Mother...

75
00:08:45.967 --> 00:08:48.651
this new school has high
standards and a good reputation...

76
00:08:49.807 --> 00:08:50.855
unlike his current school.

77
00:08:51.663 --> 00:08:53.037
The kids don't study hard enough.

78
00:08:53.807 --> 00:08:56.939
Before exams. they play around and watch TV.

79
00:08:57.167 --> 00:08:58.377
But they still get good grades.

80
00:08:59.503 --> 00:09:01.358
That means the school has low standards.

81
00:09:26.864 --> 00:09:27.627
This is Chatree.

82
00:09:29.007 --> 00:09:30.022
Your new classmate.

83
00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:33.894
Chatree will board here and study with us...

84
00:09:34.319 --> 00:09:35.661
starting from this term.

85
00:09:39.183 --> 00:09:40.077
Go take your seat.

86
00:10:08.496 --> 00:10:09.805
Chatree. Master Peng is calling.

87
00:10:13.904 --> 00:10:14.831
My name's Peng.

88
00:10:16.399 --> 00:10:17.260
That's Dr. Nui.

89
00:10:19.823 --> 00:10:21.481
This idiot is Sarote.

90
00:10:22.735 --> 00:10:24.262
That ass is Pok.

91
00:10:25.199 --> 00:10:26.093
I'm Toei.

92
00:10:30.319 --> 00:10:31.367
What's your name?

93
00:10:32.175 --> 00:10:33.069
Chatree.

94
00:10:33.839 --> 00:10:35.181
His name's Chatree.

95
00:10:35.727 --> 00:10:36.710
Okay. Chatree.

96
00:10:37.615 --> 00:10:39.655
Are you scared of ghosts?

97
00:10:40.015 --> 00:10:41.542
Of course. why wouldn't he be?

98
00:10:43.056 --> 00:10:44.648
I'm not asking you. idiot.

99
00:10:46.192 --> 00:10:47.621
Are you scared of ghosts?

100
00:10:49.839 --> 00:10:52.140
Good. As we've been here longer...

101
00:10:52.879 --> 00:10:55.083
we're gonna tell you the history of our school.

102
00:11:00.431 --> 00:11:01.893
I just found out myself.

103
00:11:02.575 --> 00:11:04.298
I'm sure you guys haven't heard it.

104
00:11:07.023 --> 00:11:09.292
A senior told me that...

105
00:11:10.095 --> 00:11:12.942
one of the cooks had a beautiful daughter.

106
00:11:16.175 --> 00:11:18.695
She was the crush of every boy in the school.

107
00:11:24.975 --> 00:11:25.771
But one day...

108
00:11:27.375 --> 00:11:29.098
she hung herself...

109
00:11:30.095 --> 00:11:31.502
from a Po tree.

110
00:11:35.311 --> 00:11:38.988
No one knew why she suddenly killed herself.

111
00:11:39.727 --> 00:11:41.734
When the police conducted an autopsy...

112
00:11:42.607 --> 00:11:44.974
they discovered that she was...

113
00:11:47.183 --> 00:11:48.492
four months pregnant.

114
00:11:51.855 --> 00:11:53.582
A pregnant ghost is the nastiest kind around.

115
00:11:54.351 --> 00:11:56.937
The story goes. a group of senior boys...

116
00:11:57.615 --> 00:11:58.760
wanted to find out the truth.

117
00:11:59.119 --> 00:12:01.486
One... two... three...

118
00:12:02.895 --> 00:12:03.756
What did they see?

119
00:12:28.751 --> 00:12:29.962
No need to go to the Po tree.

120
00:12:33.295 --> 00:12:34.408
There are ghosts in the dorm.

121
00:12:35.439 --> 00:12:36.933
Someone once saw an old man...

122
00:12:37.263 --> 00:12:38.986
walking around the dorms at night.

123
00:12:44.399 --> 00:12:46.374
At first. no one knew who he was.

124
00:12:47.311 --> 00:12:50.093
But when they looked in old yearbooks...

125
00:12:50.959 --> 00:12:51.803
they found out that...

126
00:12:52.975 --> 00:12:54.884
he used to be the dorm master.

127
00:12:59.343 --> 00:13:01.034
You've got the chills. Master Peng.

128
00:13:01.839 --> 00:13:03.181
Hey... bugger off.

129
00:13:04.015 --> 00:13:05.444
Have you guys ever noticed...

130
00:13:06.319 --> 00:13:08.588
that if you pee in the bathroom at night...

131
00:13:09.103 --> 00:13:11.274
it seems like you're not alone.

132
00:13:32.751 --> 00:13:33.449
Remember...

133
00:13:34.095 --> 00:13:36.298
Any night the dogs howl in unison...

134
00:13:36.815 --> 00:13:38.888
stay away from the bathrooms.

135
00:13:45.871 --> 00:13:46.791
Hey. do you guys know...

136
00:13:47.535 --> 00:13:49.869
why our school had to build a new swimming pool?

137
00:13:53.231 --> 00:13:54.889
Because a student drowned himself...

138
00:13:56.207 --> 00:13:58.117
in the old pool behind the school.

139
00:14:02.959 --> 00:14:03.820
Did you know...

140
00:14:04.559 --> 00:14:06.534
he was in 7th grade just like us?

141
00:14:09.103 --> 00:14:10.085
Most importantly...

142
00:14:12.111 --> 00:14:13.540
he used to board in this dorm.

143
00:14:15.343 --> 00:14:18.026
So they shut down the pool years ago.

144
00:14:19.631 --> 00:14:21.005
A senior told me that...

145
00:14:21.551 --> 00:14:24.365
Miss Pranee almost went mad.

146
00:14:28.495 --> 00:14:30.284
Yeah. that's when she became weird.

147
00:14:31.055 --> 00:14:33.356
And she still hasn't recovered.

148
00:14:34.383 --> 00:14:37.100
Do you know how weird she is?

149
00:14:42.223 --> 00:14:45.638
Have you seen the old record player in her office?

150
00:14:47.311 --> 00:14:49.732
She likes to listen to this one sappy love song.

151
00:14:51.375 --> 00:14:52.749
It gives me the creeps.

152
00:14:56.975 --> 00:14:58.568
One day...

153
00:15:00.111 --> 00:15:00.776
someone saw...

154
00:15:01.615 --> 00:15:04.462
Miss Pranee staring and crying at an open drawer.

155
00:15:20.943 --> 00:15:22.023
To this day...

156
00:15:22.479 --> 00:15:23.624
nobody knows...

157
00:15:24.111 --> 00:15:26.980
what the hell is in that drawer.

158
00:15:27.759 --> 00:15:28.834
Maybe there's a magic genie.

159
00:15:29.711 --> 00:15:31.751
Magic genie. my ass.

160
00:15:36.943 --> 00:15:37.804
After awhile...

161
00:15:38.831 --> 00:15:40.653
you'll see for yourself. Chatree.

162
00:15:47.855 --> 00:15:48.553
I bet that...

163
00:15:49.263 --> 00:15:54.697
Miss Pranee had something
to do with the boy's death.

164
00:15:56.111 --> 00:15:58.794
And that boy's ghost is a vicious one.

165
00:15:59.791 --> 00:16:01.165
Anyone who slept in his bed...

166
00:16:01.582 --> 00:16:04.233
was kicked out of it every night.

167
00:16:04.911 --> 00:16:07.278
Finally. they had to put the bed in the storage.

168
00:16:10.735 --> 00:16:11.269
But...

169
00:16:13.006 --> 00:16:17.709
I saw the janitor bring his
bed out from the storage today.

170
00:16:19.791 --> 00:16:20.270
Boys!

171
00:16:21.711 --> 00:16:23.085
Bed time is for sleeping.

172
00:16:23.951 --> 00:16:25.674
Anyone who can't wake up tomorrow...

173
00:16:26.639 --> 00:16:27.588
will get whacked.

174
00:19:18.734 --> 00:19:20.676
Hey... the new kid wet his bed!

175
00:19:20.847 --> 00:19:24.906
All grown up and still wetting his bed.

176
00:19:25.551 --> 00:19:28.682
The new boy wet his bed!

177
00:19:39.854 --> 00:19:40.454
Damn it!

178
00:20:06.415 --> 00:20:08.171
Hey... if you hang it up that way...

179
00:20:08.431 --> 00:20:09.772
it'll just fall to the ground.

180
00:20:11.342 --> 00:20:13.895
The clothesline is a battle zone.

181
00:20:14.351 --> 00:20:16.839
If you're going to make space you have to be tricky.

182
00:20:20.334 --> 00:20:22.062
And you only need one pair of bathing shorts.

183
00:20:22.223 --> 00:20:25.768
One pair will suffice.
Or else every pair will get moldy.

184
00:20:46.799 --> 00:20:48.173
Hey. do you guys smell something?

185
00:20:50.127 --> 00:20:50.759
No...

186
00:20:52.366 --> 00:20:53.260
That's not it.

187
00:21:02.799 --> 00:21:04.140
I know. It reeks of his piss.

188
00:21:05.454 --> 00:21:08.520
I see all the ghost stories
made you wet your pants.

189
00:21:11.343 --> 00:21:13.230
Make fun of the new boy. everyone.

190
00:21:19.598 --> 00:21:21.038
Pok. why are you laughing?

191
00:21:21.039 --> 00:21:22.458
Your mouth stinks pretty bad as well.

192
00:21:27.151 --> 00:21:27.914
Is it broken?

193
00:21:29.039 --> 00:21:30.697
I don't know. Maybe I can fix it.

194
00:21:32.015 --> 00:21:32.997
You know how to fix it?

195
00:21:34.670 --> 00:21:36.012
I'm not sure but I'll try.

196
00:21:38.446 --> 00:21:39.526
Can I try playing it?

197
00:21:40.206 --> 00:21:40.686
Sure.

198
00:21:41.807 --> 00:21:44.457
Chatree. you have a phone call.

199
00:21:45.166 --> 00:21:46.213
It's your dad.

200
00:21:56.015 --> 00:22:00.750
Chatree Anantpitisuk. your
father is on the dormitory phone.

201
00:22:01.294 --> 00:22:05.386
Chatree Anantpitisuk. your
father is on the dormitory phone.

202
00:22:17.071 --> 00:22:18.150
I brought you some sweets.

203
00:22:40.879 --> 00:22:42.220
Don't let me catch you again.

204
00:22:42.734 --> 00:22:44.458
If you get bad grades this year...

205
00:22:44.590 --> 00:22:45.539
I'll really punish you.

206
00:23:08.142 --> 00:23:10.052
Chatree isn't here right now.

207
00:23:10.766 --> 00:23:12.071
Would you like to leave a message?

208
00:23:14.735 --> 00:23:16.873
No. that's okay. I'll call back another day.

209
00:23:17.422 --> 00:23:18.698
Thank you.

210
00:25:41.774 --> 00:25:42.756
Hey... who's there!

211
00:25:43.279 --> 00:25:44.075
Open the door!

212
00:25:46.574 --> 00:25:48.461
Asshole. just wait until I get out!

213
00:25:49.966 --> 00:25:50.664
Hey!

214
00:25:51.630 --> 00:25:52.775
Open the door!

215
00:25:59.406 --> 00:26:00.551
That was awesome.

216
00:26:00.686 --> 00:26:02.628
Just a few ghost tales and he peed his pants.

217
00:26:02.991 --> 00:26:04.398
What a sucker!

218
00:26:13.230 --> 00:26:14.278
Hey. open it please.

219
00:29:24.654 --> 00:29:25.133
Hey...

220
00:29:26.318 --> 00:29:27.081
Woke up late?

221
00:29:27.758 --> 00:29:28.238
Yeah.

222
00:29:32.750 --> 00:29:35.597
You're real curious about Miss Pranee. aren't you?

223
00:29:36.942 --> 00:29:37.890
Watch out. okay.

224
00:29:42.734 --> 00:29:43.213
Sure.

225
00:29:43.918 --> 00:29:46.601
Do you know why Miss Pranee's so weird?

226
00:29:48.942 --> 00:29:50.153
There are lots of theories.

227
00:29:51.182 --> 00:29:52.742
Worst of all are the ghost stories.

228
00:29:53.486 --> 00:29:54.435
They're not true.

229
00:29:56.078 --> 00:29:56.939
Been here long?

230
00:29:58.894 --> 00:29:59.625
Yeah. why?

231
00:30:01.614 --> 00:30:02.345
No reason.

232
00:30:02.926 --> 00:30:03.941
You seem to know it all.

233
00:30:04.974 --> 00:30:06.119
Of course I do!

234
00:30:06.414 --> 00:30:09.927
Don't you know I'm
Vichien 'Know-lt-All' Chumchong!

235
00:30:11.374 --> 00:30:13.000
Hurry up and take a bath.

236
00:30:13.390 --> 00:30:14.427
Miss Pranee is coming down.

237
00:30:22.606 --> 00:30:24.067
Before we go down for breakfast...

238
00:30:25.006 --> 00:30:26.348
I have something to say.

239
00:30:28.014 --> 00:30:30.403
This is a school not a graveyard.

240
00:30:32.174 --> 00:30:35.490
I want you to stop telling
ghost stories to scare each other.

241
00:30:37.838 --> 00:30:41.450
If I catch anyone engaging in such nonsense...

242
00:30:43.054 --> 00:30:44.647
don't say you weren't warned.

243
00:30:50.446 --> 00:30:52.682
Chatree. wait up!

244
00:30:54.125 --> 00:30:55.315
What are you daydreaming about?

245
00:31:04.238 --> 00:31:05.543
Have you ever snuck out of school?

246
00:31:06.990 --> 00:31:07.688
Where to?

247
00:31:08.654 --> 00:31:09.385
Home. of course.

248
00:31:11.246 --> 00:31:11.726
What for?

249
00:31:12.206 --> 00:31:13.319
School is more fun than home.

250
00:31:13.998 --> 00:31:15.591
No parents to tell you what to do.

251
00:31:16.622 --> 00:31:17.702
Fun as hell. it is.

252
00:31:21.294 --> 00:31:23.021
It's hard at first but you'll get used to it.

253
00:31:25.262 --> 00:31:26.342
No. I won't.

254
00:31:31.054 --> 00:31:32.069
Do you see what I see?

255
00:31:35.182 --> 00:31:35.661
Geese?

256
00:31:37.870 --> 00:31:38.437
Look again.

257
00:31:41.454 --> 00:31:43.527
Oh... there are goose eggs!

258
00:31:47.374 --> 00:31:48.935
Calm down. little bro.

259
00:31:51.150 --> 00:31:52.972
Geese are really protective of their eggs.

260
00:31:54.478 --> 00:31:55.972
If you want to steal them...

261
00:31:56.974 --> 00:31:58.021
there's only one way.

262
00:32:01.422 --> 00:32:02.502
Hurry up. man.

263
00:32:09.613 --> 00:32:10.279
Hurry up!

264
00:32:11.630 --> 00:32:12.296
Hurry!

265
00:32:17.486 --> 00:32:18.152
Hurry!

266
00:32:25.742 --> 00:32:26.690
I got them!

267
00:32:31.502 --> 00:32:32.330
Chatree...

268
00:32:36.141 --> 00:32:37.352
your father's on the phone.

269
00:32:42.605 --> 00:32:43.499
Hold on. please.

270
00:32:43.662 --> 00:32:44.229
Yes.

271
00:32:46.734 --> 00:32:47.693
I'll see you later. okay.

272
00:32:48.142 --> 00:32:48.709
Sure.

273
00:34:24.654 --> 00:34:27.883
Chatree. grab a seat for us
in the courtyard after dinner.

