Idiots! I fooled you!

549
01:16:05.835 --> 01:16:08.072
You were faking it? That's pretty funny.

550
01:16:23.659 --> 01:16:24.935
Did you do your homework yet?

551
01:16:25.355 --> 01:16:27.178
I forgot. It's due first period too.

552
01:16:31.819 --> 01:16:32.801
Help me!

553
01:16:33.771 --> 01:16:35.626
Hey... Vichien is drowning.

554
01:16:36.075 --> 01:16:37.058
Help me!

555
01:16:40.619 --> 01:16:42.180
Go ahead and save him.

556
01:16:42.859 --> 01:16:44.069
But he could be faking it.

557
01:16:47.275 --> 01:16:48.322
Help me!

558
01:17:02.539 --> 01:17:03.750
Help me!

559
01:17:05.996 --> 01:17:08.134
Hey. it's 6 PM. Let's head back.

560
01:17:20.523 --> 01:17:22.017
Let's go.

561
01:17:27.691 --> 01:17:28.935
Hey. I'm leaving now.

562
01:17:48.811 --> 01:17:51.877
Then how come they say that...

563
01:17:52.171 --> 01:17:54.506
Miss Pranee was related to your death?

564
01:17:59.211 --> 01:18:01.218
You read that newspaper. right?

565
01:18:09.003 --> 01:18:10.628
It's about my father.

566
01:18:11.371 --> 01:18:13.510
Miss Pranee didn't want me to find out.

567
01:18:18.411 --> 01:18:19.207
Vichien!

568
01:18:20.811 --> 01:18:21.793
What are you doing?

569
01:18:22.827 --> 01:18:24.094
Who gave you permission to enter?

570
01:18:24.555 --> 01:18:25.483
Come here.

571
01:18:25.963 --> 01:18:28.865
Why did you do this? Why?

572
01:18:33.547 --> 01:18:35.402
I'll hit you until I break your hand.

573
01:18:39.307 --> 01:18:41.347
I just wanted to read the news about my father.

574
01:18:46.123 --> 01:18:49.058
Unfortunately. Miss Pranee caught me first.

575
01:18:51.435 --> 01:18:53.857
Miss Pranee. Vichien hasn't
returned to the dorm yet.

576
01:19:27.339 --> 01:19:29.346
Before my accident...

577
01:19:30.155 --> 01:19:32.937
I managed to sneak back
in to steal the newspaper.

578
01:19:42.475 --> 01:19:43.850
Ever since then...

579
01:19:44.907 --> 01:19:47.689
Miss Pranee has thought that my death...

580
01:19:48.427 --> 01:19:49.638
was her fault.

581
01:20:05.451 --> 01:20:07.426
But how come you have to drown...

582
01:20:08.139 --> 01:20:09.863
over and over like this?

583
01:20:11.819 --> 01:20:12.747
I don't know.

584
01:20:14.571 --> 01:20:17.538
How much longer will you be stuck like this?

585
01:20:18.955 --> 01:20:20.265
I don't know myself.

586
01:20:22.059 --> 01:20:25.671
But it's really cold at the bottom.

587
01:20:55.787 --> 01:20:58.176
See... didn't I tell you...

588
01:20:58.795 --> 01:21:02.690
that it must be the boy who drowned in the pool.

589
01:21:04.363 --> 01:21:07.363
I've seen ghosts like this before.

590
01:21:10.187 --> 01:21:11.649
At my old house...

591
01:21:12.331 --> 01:21:15.779
a motorcycle crashed
rounding the corner one night.

592
01:21:21.867 --> 01:21:25.096
The driver flew off his bike and died instantly.

593
01:21:26.667 --> 01:21:27.812
After that...

594
01:21:28.651 --> 01:21:31.334
I'd hear the same motorbike...

595
01:21:31.562 --> 01:21:34.018
skid around the corner almost every night.

596
01:22:09.355 --> 01:22:13.217
As if the spirit hadn't been reborn yet...

597
01:22:13.706 --> 01:22:15.299
so it had to re-enact it's death...

598
01:22:15.659 --> 01:22:19.336
over and over.

599
01:22:37.995 --> 01:22:38.824
What then?

600
01:22:39.691 --> 01:22:41.513
We moved the heck out of there.

601
01:22:42.154 --> 01:22:43.300
No...

602
01:22:43.595 --> 01:22:45.417
How do we help the spirits get reborn...

603
01:22:45.482 --> 01:22:47.094
so they stop re-enacting their own deaths?

604
01:22:47.691 --> 01:22:51.750
Ghosts and humans occupy separate worlds.

605
01:22:52.587 --> 01:22:54.856
To help a ghost you must be a ghost.

606
01:22:56.107 --> 01:22:58.278
To be a ghost. you have to die first.

607
01:22:59.051 --> 01:23:02.728
Unless you can split your spirit from your body.

608
01:24:08.650 --> 01:24:09.479
Are you crazy?

609
01:24:09.962 --> 01:24:11.751
Why would you want to die?

610
01:24:15.915 --> 01:24:16.547
Ton...

611
01:24:17.355 --> 01:24:19.111
swear that you won't do it.

612
01:24:25.675 --> 01:24:27.563
Hey. promise me.

613
01:24:31.435 --> 01:24:33.257
Dr. Nui. what the hell are you looking at?

614
01:24:34.730 --> 01:24:36.454
Something's wrong with Chatree.

615
01:24:37.067 --> 01:24:38.015
He seems strange.

616
01:24:39.563 --> 01:24:41.366
Shit. the other day you said he wasn't strange.

617
01:24:42.250 --> 01:24:43.046
I know.

618
01:24:44.715 --> 01:24:47.879
But today he seems strange.

619
01:24:48.651 --> 01:24:49.480
Maybe...

620
01:24:49.899 --> 01:24:51.492
he's going to jump off the building.

621
01:24:52.618 --> 01:24:55.106
How the hell can he jump through the grille?

622
01:25:03.819 --> 01:25:05.128
Can you see that water tank?

623
01:25:07.435 --> 01:25:09.377
I've climbed to the top before.

624
01:25:10.283 --> 01:25:11.843
The view is even nicer from up there.

625
01:25:15.435 --> 01:25:16.711
I'll take you there some day.

626
01:25:42.730 --> 01:25:45.119
Chatree has disappeared.

627
01:25:57.451 --> 01:25:59.239
Playing during dinner again?

628
01:25:59.627 --> 01:26:01.993
You'll see... I'll teach you a lesson.

629
01:26:38.058 --> 01:26:39.335
Hey. Chatree! Chatree!

630
01:26:42.922 --> 01:26:44.449
Chatree. are you okay?

631
01:26:44.586 --> 01:26:45.350
Chatree. wake up!

632
01:26:51.947 --> 01:26:52.808
Killed himself. right?

633
01:26:54.411 --> 01:26:54.978
No.

634
01:26:56.010 --> 01:26:57.961
I think he split his spirit from his body.

635
01:26:57.962 --> 01:26:59.177
What are you talking about?

636
01:26:59.178 --> 01:27:00.253
Splitting spirits from what?

637
01:27:00.906 --> 01:27:02.117
He told me himself...

638
01:27:02.603 --> 01:27:05.636
that he wanted to help his
friend that drowned in the pool.

639
01:27:06.570 --> 01:27:08.959
I suggested he could if
he split his spirit from his body.

640
01:27:21.483 --> 01:27:22.213
Trust me...

641
01:27:22.795 --> 01:27:24.223
we have to take him to the old pool.

642
01:27:26.218 --> 01:27:28.323
Miss Pranee. Chatree killed himself.

643
01:28:02.954 --> 01:28:04.580
Vichien's drowning!

644
01:28:11.146 --> 01:28:11.626
Help me!

645
01:28:46.666 --> 01:28:47.615
Here!

646
01:28:48.139 --> 01:28:49.000
What's that for?

647
01:28:49.419 --> 01:28:51.207
You idiot! To break the lock!

648
01:29:08.971 --> 01:29:09.865
What do we do now?

649
01:29:24.075 --> 01:29:26.246
You told me that no one cares about you.

650
01:29:27.242 --> 01:29:28.104
How about yourself?

651
01:29:28.779 --> 01:29:30.428
Do you care about anyone else but yourself?

652
01:29:39.595 --> 01:29:41.831
Hey... let me out!

653
01:30:24.970 --> 01:30:26.530
Are you still mad at your friends...

654
01:30:26.666 --> 01:30:28.193
for not saving you from drowning?

655
01:30:28.778 --> 01:30:29.760
No. I'm not mad anymore.

656
01:30:32.650 --> 01:30:33.282
How about you?

657
01:30:33.803 --> 01:30:35.414
Do you still want to run away from school?

658
01:30:36.235 --> 01:30:37.413
No. not anymore.

659
01:30:37.995 --> 01:30:40.842
If I did. I would run straight to Namtarn's embrace.

660
01:30:42.443 --> 01:30:44.548
Hey. hey... I know what you're thinking.

661
01:30:44.875 --> 01:30:47.264
Don't get me started! I saw
the way you looked at her. too.

662
01:30:47.499 --> 01:30:49.059
I've had my heart set on her for years.

663
01:30:50.250 --> 01:30:51.592
When will we go visit her again?

664
01:31:00.587 --> 01:31:02.147
Hey... Ton...

665
01:31:08.619 --> 01:31:09.895
I've got to leave now.

666
01:32:11.338 --> 01:32:12.413
Hey... Chatree is coming to.

667
01:32:13.162 --> 01:32:15.072
Chatree! Chatree is coming to.

668
01:32:15.563 --> 01:32:16.456
Are you okay. Chatree?

669
01:32:17.131 --> 01:32:19.040
Chatree. are you okay? Chatree...

670
01:32:19.915 --> 01:32:21.027
How are you. Chatree?

671
01:32:23.755 --> 01:32:24.810
You're fine now.

672
01:32:24.811 --> 01:32:25.886
Hey... he's come to already?

673
01:32:28.426 --> 01:32:30.433
Miss Pranee. Chatree is fine now.

674
01:33:18.986 --> 01:33:21.255
I never knew our school was this big.

675
01:33:22.794 --> 01:33:25.609
Why are you so amazed by the size of our school?

676
01:33:26.218 --> 01:33:27.527
I know from experience.

677
01:33:27.850 --> 01:33:30.152
Miss Pranee made me run
around the school before.

678
01:33:30.762 --> 01:33:32.289
Tears are falling from my eyes.

679
01:33:32.810 --> 01:33:34.469
You're the one who's going to fall.

680
01:33:35.306 --> 01:33:36.582
Okay. calm down.

681
01:33:37.354 --> 01:33:38.467
I was only kidding.

682
01:33:41.642 --> 01:33:42.570
Hey. Ton...

683
01:33:43.754 --> 01:33:45.990
why didn't you tell Miss Pranee
the truth about Vichien?

684
01:33:46.826 --> 01:33:49.575
Yeah. instead of letting us all get punished.

685
01:33:53.898 --> 01:33:55.556
I don't think she'd believe me.

686
01:33:57.706 --> 01:34:01.001
But... we all believe you.

687
01:34:01.546 --> 01:34:04.132
If you happen to see another ghost...

688
01:34:05.002 --> 01:34:07.272
feel free to consult me. okay?

689
01:34:07.787 --> 01:34:09.445
But don't consult me. okay?

690
01:34:10.378 --> 01:34:12.745
Let me be the first one to consult you then.

691
01:34:13.770 --> 01:34:15.842
Why the heck do you speak with a lisp?

692
01:34:25.130 --> 01:34:34.371
Chatree Anantpitisuk. please meet
your parents in the dorm.

693
01:34:35.530 --> 01:34:37.056
I guess I'm off.

694
01:34:39.754 --> 01:34:41.183
See you guys next year.

695
01:34:44.938 --> 01:34:45.636
Good luck. man.

696
01:34:45.962 --> 01:34:46.977
Good luck.

697
01:35:00.842 --> 01:35:03.492
Ton. take me to see the swimming pool. please!

698
01:35:03.786 --> 01:35:06.120
Be patient. Toh. Let him pack his things first.

699
01:35:06.282 --> 01:35:07.591
Okay. but then can we see it?

700
01:35:07.818 --> 01:35:08.417
Yes. dear.

701
01:35:13.386 --> 01:35:15.208
Have you been eating enough food?

702
01:35:16.298 --> 01:35:18.470
You've gotten darker.

703
01:35:19.114 --> 01:35:21.001
And lost weight as well.

704
01:35:21.002 --> 01:35:22.729
You've been playing outdoors too much. right?

705
01:35:26.155 --> 01:35:27.583
Mom. you're embarrassing me.

706
01:35:28.426 --> 01:35:29.572
Why be embarrassed?

707
01:35:29.770 --> 01:35:32.705
When you're older I won't get to hug you anymore.

708
01:35:36.906 --> 01:35:38.630
Toh. stay around here. okay.

709
01:35:40.042 --> 01:35:41.537
Let's get your bags. dear.

710
01:36:03.370 --> 01:36:04.264
Dad...

711
01:36:06.890 --> 01:36:08.166
I like this school now.

712
01:36:41.194 --> 01:36:41.990
Miss Pranee...

713
01:36:49.066 --> 01:36:50.757
Vichien didn't kill himself.

714
01:36:55.210 --> 01:36:58.985
His drowning was really an accident.

715
01:37:07.530 --> 01:37:09.090
Vichien asked me to apologize...

716
01:37:10.730 --> 01:37:12.705
for breaking your record player that day.

717
01:37:21.162 --> 01:37:22.144
He knows that...

718
01:37:23.594 --> 01:37:25.382
you were concerned about him.

719
01:37:34.506 --> 01:37:35.488
Thank you. Miss Pranee...

720
01:37:35.850 --> 01:37:37.411
for always taking care of us.

721
01:37:39.849 --> 01:37:41.039
See you next year. Miss Pranee.

722
01:38:24.009 --> 01:38:27.141
I still remember the first
day my father took me home.

723
01:38:30.121 --> 01:38:33.537
It was a Friday afternoon much like any other.

724
01:38:35.082 --> 01:38:38.245
But something had changed inside of me.

725
01:38:40.329 --> 01:38:42.501
That term. I only grew two centimeters.

726
01:38:43.465 --> 01:38:45.288
It'll be a while before I'm a grown man.

727
01:38:48.617 --> 01:38:52.480
Being friends with Vichien
has taught me many things.

728
01:39:08.810 --> 01:39:09.792
I didn't know...

729
01:39:11.274 --> 01:39:14.470
what adventures the next term had in store.

730
01:39:16.170 --> 01:39:18.755
But I knew that wanted to rejoin my gang of friends.

731
01:39:19.978 --> 01:39:23.840
Because I've learned that
with one close friend by your side...

732
01:39:24.810 --> 01:39:27.079
even the worst things in life...

733
01:39:27.721 --> 01:39:30.536
will eventually pass...

734
01:39:31.370 --> 01:39:33.224
in just one short breath.

735
01:39:34.305 --> 01:40:34.646
